id: pm-2ldo
title: "GH-485: pm search rewrites quoted status:all hybrid queries into --status and drops keywords"
description: "Quoted hybrid queries beginning with an inline status: filter are rewritten into a --status flag whose value swallows the remaining keywords, leaving no positional keywords and failing the command. Reproduced on 2026.7.9."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[5]: agent-ux,"area:search",cli,gh-issue,parser
created_at: "2026-07-09T10:33:07.477Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-09T17:03:11.161Z"
closed_at: "2026-07-09T17:03:10.538Z"
author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 90
acceptance_criteria: "pm search \"status:all scene grounding\" applies the status filter and treats remaining tokens as keywords; regression test covers inline-filter-first quoted queries; if a query is inline-filter-only, the error names the inline-filter syntax rather than a generic missing-keywords message"
parent: pm-ydp6
risk: medium
confidence: high
