  "2026-07-09T17:03:09.910Z",claude-code-agent,"Verification: unquoted search inline filters now stay query input and are parsed by runSearch; focused bootstrap/search tests passed, manual temp PM_PATH proof found the expected item for pm search 'status:all scene grounding --json', full coverage passed 5480 tests at 100/100/100/100, and the CI static sequence passed."
